#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a table of up to ten high scores for the currently selected game. Each "
"line shows the player's rank and name, the level reached, the score "
"achieved, the day of the week and the date."
msgstr ""
"Näitab tabelit parajasti valitud mängu kuni kümne parema tulemusega. Igal "
"real on ära toodud mängija koht ja nimi, saavutatud tase, kogutud "
"punktisumma, nädalapäev ja kuupäev."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>Q</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kill Hero</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>Q</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Mäng</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Tapa kangelane</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kills the hero when he is in a position from which he cannot escape."
msgstr ""
"Tapab kangelase, mis on abiks eriti siis, kui kangelane on sattunud "
"positsiooni, kust ta enam välja ei pääse."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Mäng</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Välju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Terminates &kgoldrunner; immediately. If a game is in progress, it "
"disappears forever (unless you have just saved it) and there is no check for "
"a high score. If you were editing a level, you are given an opportunity to "
"save your work."
msgstr ""
"Lõpetab otsekohe &kgoldrunner;i töö. Kui mäng on parajasti pooleli, kaob see "
"igaveseks (kui sa ei ole seda just varem salvestanud) ning rekord jäetakse "
"arvestamata (eeldusel muidugi, et oled rekordini jõudnud, millisel juhul on "
"väheusutav, et sa seda võimalust kasutad :-) Kui tegemist on taseme "
"redigeerimisega, pakutakse sulle võimalust tehtud muudatused salvestada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Move Menu"
msgstr "Menüü Liikumine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:915
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "All the demo and replay moves will replay previously recorded levels. All "
#| "can be interrupted and stopped by clicking on the playing area with the "
#| "mouse, pressing the spacebar or selecting a menu item or shortcut (such "
#| "as <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Game...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgid ""
"All the demo and replay moves will replay previously recorded levels. All "
"can be interrupted and stopped by clicking on the playing area with the "
"mouse, pressing the &Space; bar or selecting a menu item or shortcut (such "
"as <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Game…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Kõik demo ja korduste käigud mängivad läbi varem salvestatud tasemeid. Kõiki "
"neid saab katkestada ja peatada, kui klõpsata mängualale hiirega, vajutada "
"tühikuklahvi või valida sobiv menüükäsk või kiirklahv (näiteks "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Mäng</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uus mäng...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Vihje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a popup hint, if there is one for the level being played. By "
"convention, Championship and Tutorial games have hints on every level. Other "
"games rarely have hints. The lower part of the &kgoldrunner; window shows "
"whether a hint is available or not."
msgstr ""
"Näitab vihjet, kui see on mängitava taseme kohta olemas. Reeglina on "
"meistritaseme ja treeningmängudel vihjed iga taseme kohta. Teistes mängudes "
"leidub vihjeid harva. &kgoldrunner;i akna allosas näeb, kas vihjeid on või "
"mitte."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Liikumine</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plays a demonstration of play in a few recorded levels. These are the same "
"as in the startup demo."
msgstr ""
"Esitab mängu mõne salvestatud taseme demonstratsiooni. Need on samasugused, "
"nagu näidatakse käivitusaegses demos."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:948
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show A Solution...</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show a Solution</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Näita lahendust...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replays a recorded solution of a level, if there is a solution on file in "
"the released game-data."
msgstr ""
"Esitab taseme salvestatud lahenduse, kui see leidub mänguandmete failis."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Instant Replay</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Liikumine</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Viimane uuesti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stops play in the current level and replays the recorded version from the "
"beginning. If you interrupt the replay, you can continue playing from that "
"point and try another approach. You can use this feature to build up a "
"winning sequence of moves in stages, but that will invalidate any high score "
"you might be working on."
msgstr ""
"Peatab aktiivse taseme mängimise ja esitab selle salvestatud versiooni "
"algusest peale. Kui korduse katkestad, võid jätkata mängimist peatuskohast "
"ja valida teistsuguse käitumise. Sel moel saab katse-eksituse meetodil leida "
"võiduka lahenduse, kuid samas ei võeta sel juhul saavutatud tulemust arvesse "
"edetabelis."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Replay Last Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Liikumine</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Viimane tase uuesti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replays the recorded version of the last level you played, from the "
"beginning (&eg; if you lost the level). If you interrupt the replay, you can "
"continue playing from that point and try another approach. You can use this "
"feature to build up a winning sequence of moves in stages, but that will "
"invalidate any high score you might be working on."
msgstr ""
"Kordab viimast salvestatud mängitud taset algusest peale (kui &eg; oled "
"taseme kaotanud). Kui korduse katkestad, võid jätkata mängimist peatuskohast "
"ja valida teistsuguse käitumise. Sel moel saab katse-eksituse meetodil leida "
"võiduka lahenduse, kuid samas ei võeta sel juhul saavutatud tulemust arvesse "
"edetabelis."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Replay Any Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Valitud tase uuesti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replays the recorded version of any level you have previously played."
msgstr "Kordab mis tahes varem mängitud salvestatud taset."

